servers.description:
NOW ON 1.14! Foxes, pillagers, pandas, and more!

Applecraft is a survival server that offers ranks and extra /sethomes for voting, grief protection, custom player shops and friendly staff!

We preserve your survival experience, and do not allow raiding or griefing, which means all your builds are completely safe. If you like pure survival, this is the server for you!

Each vote gets you closer to the next rank up, and each new rank gets you an extra /sethome.

Use the wild warp waterfall at spawn to get far away and start your game! It sends you somewhere within a 20,000 block radius of spawn.

The world border is 100,000 blocks so there are plenty of unexplored biomes to discover and build in!

Also make sure to visit our player shops, where you can try your hand at making your own fortune by trading with other players.

servers.description:
»»» FriendlyMC ««« | Friendly Minecraft survival for all!

In need of a family-friendly vanilla server? Look no further! We are a community that loves to survive, grind, interact, and play together with friends. We love our community of players and seek to give them the best survival vanilla experience out there. We take and consider all suggestions, love to host events, and see the server grow. Features of the server are Anti-Grief, Land Claiming, Very Specific Rules, Crates, Good Economy, and much more. If you play FriendlyMC, expect many features to be added and a friendly community and staff team who love to see new players come and join in with the community. Come check us out! There is nothing to lose!

We here on FriendlyMC are a server that cares a lot about its community. Whether it's making our donor ranks affordable, or making it a fun experience for those who don't want to spend a single penny. We appreciate the whole community and just playing the server helps us out and means a lot to the staff. The staff looks to know all of the players very well. The dedicated staff love to take your suggestions to help build on the server and make it better.

[ Discord: https://discord.gg/Jyunu9u
Server IP: FriendlyMC.xyz ]

Looking for an amazing vanilla server with great staff, a welcoming community, and just a bunch of fun? FriendlyMC is here to offer just that. Here are a few of the things we have to offer:

[+] Anti-Grief/Land-Claiming | Players can claim their land with "Claim Blocks". Claim blocks on our server will not be hard to get. With that being said, there will be multiple ways for players, LIKE YOU, to earn loads of claim blocks in order to secure your claims from those PESKY griefers. Can't afford to claim ALL of your land right away? That's no problem, our rules enforce that stealing and griefing is not allowed. If you suspect your land was griefed and/or stolen from, please contact the staff via tickets on our discord.

[+] Discord Chat to MC Chat, or Vice Versa! | When you join our discord, you may notice we have an in-game chat channel. This is a channel that allows players to communicate with each other in-game, and to discord. Players who do the steps at the bottom of this post will be granted the correct role and be allowed to send messages inside of that channel!

[+] Beta | Our server's release was 4/13/2020. We plan to keep the server as long as we can. During this time, we will consider this season, or map, the "beta" version. As there's no reset date for our server as of now, whenever a reset happens, the beta will be over and the official release will happen.


[+] PVP | PVP in all survival worlds is disabled. This allows safe game-play while you try and survive! Though there's currently no way to PVP right now, there will be a PVP world created. Here will allow players to venture off and PVP members of our server!!!

Discord: https://discord.gg/Jyunu9u
